Union ParseResult has value value: i32; error code: u8 and offset: i32.

To main, giving i32.
Let result be ParseResult.error with code be 2 and offset be 8.
Let total be 0.
Let errors be 0.
Match result:
ParseResult.value with value: total becomes total plus value;
ParseResult.error with code as c and offset as pos: errors becomes errors plus (c as i32) plus pos;
otherwise: total becomes total.
Give total plus errors.
